author: COMSOL
description:
An eigenfrequency analysis of the vibration modes of a circular disk backed by a cylindrical cavity shows that you cannot neglect the coupling between the bending modes of the disk and the acoustic modes in the cylinder. The results correlate well with semi-analytical and experimental data.

Requires the Acoustics Module and the Structural Mechanics Module.
label: coupled_vibrations.mph
